<h1 class="csh-font-sans-bold">Como criar um novo agendamento?</h1></div><div role="article" class="csh-article-content-text csh-article-content-text-large">Um novo agendamento pode ser criado a partir das seguintes tarefas:<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="*" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Ligação</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="*" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Follow up</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="*" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Visita</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="*" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Reunião</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="*" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-list">Proposta</span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Para criar um novo agendamento, clique em <span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-bold csh-font-sans-medium">Leads</span> presente no menu esquerdo.<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/leads_7mtgql.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Escolha o lead e selecione a tarefa que você deseja agendar. <br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/agendar_we1pwu.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Após escolher a tarefa, escreva o motivo do agendamento, escolha a data e clique em salvar.<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/definir-agendamento-tarefa_1e3rgw6.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/>Prontinho, agora seu agendamento já estará no seu calendário.<br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-image"><img src="https://storage.crisp.chat/users/helpdesk/website/3f2b13ba09ee9e0/agendamentos-no-calendario_d02qaz.png" alt="" loading="lazy"/></span><br class="csh-new-line"/><br class="csh-new-line"/><span data-type="|" class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-emphasis csh-font-sans-medium">Depois de cumprir com o agendamento, lembre-se de marcar como finalizado.</span><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-line csh-article-content-separate csh-article-content-separate-top"></span><p class="csh-article-content-updated csh-text-wrap csh-font-sans-light">Atualizado em: 06/03/2020</p><span class="csh-markdown csh-markdown-line csh-article-content-separate csh-article-content-separate-bottom"></span></div></article><section data-has-answer="false" role="none" class="csh-article-rate"></body></html>